	<text xml:lang="la">
		<body>
			<div>
				<p>
					<s n="1" xml:lang="la" type="auto">S.</s>
					<s n="2" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Quanta in sollicitudine, reverendissime pater, hosce dies fuerim, cogitare potes ipse lectis Germanicis literis, quas simul mitto; eas tu quidem difficillime leges (scripsit eas <persName type="citizen_name" ref="p1770" cert="high">Georgius Carlin</persName>, qui pessime pingit), eas tamen tibi mittere volui, ut narrationi meae fidem facerem.</s>
					<s n="3" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Summa: principem <placeName type="auto_name">Condensem</placeName> in colloquio circumventum a <persName type="auto_name">Guisiano</persName> pugione percussum, cecidisse simul utrinque 300.</s>
					<s n="4" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Haec ille, qui <persName type="citizen_name" ref="p1770" cert="high">Carlino</persName> dixit (existimamus autem esse <placeName type="citizen_name">Dietägium</placeName>) affirmavit <placeName ref="l1107" cert="high">Tridento</placeName> per postam in <placeName ref="l822" type="auto_name">Germaniam</placeName> missa.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="5" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Quaeso te, pater, tu nos hac cura et angore libera.</s>
					<s n="6" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Verisimile quidem non est citius haec <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l1107" cert="high">Tridenti</placeName> et in <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l822" cert="high">Germania</placeName> nunciata quam <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l760">Solothuri</placeName>; sed tamen quid non timemus amantes?</s>
					<s n="7" xml:lang="la" type="auto">aut quid adversarii non audent?</s>
					<s n="8" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Deinde addit in literis pro certo exercitum <persName ref="p18477" cert="high">Ferdinandi</persName> contra <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l2510" cert="high">Turcam</placeName> missum esse deletum et in hoc 400 equites.</s>
					<s n="9" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Quae mandasti, maiori curae mihi esse non possunt; scripsi in plura simul loca.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="10" xml:lang="la" type="auto"><persName type="citizen_name" ref="p8114">Balingketus</persName> praeterea singulariter promisit operam; interim et hic apud papistas meos habebo exploratores.</s>
					<s n="11" xml:lang="la" type="auto"><persName type="citizen_name" ref="p3375" cert="high">Vergerius</persName> heri <placeName ref="l93" cert="high">Clavenna</placeName> rediit.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="12" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Nondum conveni hominem; vides, quibus elogiis eum ornet senex <persName type="citizen_name" ref="p2019">Maynardus</persName>; quod ex specula prospexi et illis ecclesiis ominatus sum, res testatur etc.</s>
					<s n="13" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Non est, quod vel <persName ref="p18700" cert="high">Augustini</persName> vel <persName type="citizen_name" ref="p1770" cert="high">Carlini</persName> literas remittas; discerpe tamen.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="14" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Collega dicit <persName type="citizen_name" ref="p3375">Vergerium</persName> dicere pontificem exercitum in <placeName ref="l834" type="auto_name">Italia</placeName> conscribere.</s>
					<s n="15" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Venit alius <placeName ref="l522" cert="high">Venetiis</placeName>, qui idem refert.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="16" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Novi praeterea habetur plane nihil.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="17" xml:lang="la" type="auto" ana="farewell">Vale, reverende pater, cum tuis omnibus.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="18" xml:lang="la" type="auto"><placeName ref="l98" cert="high">Curię</placeName> 18. maii anno 1562.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="19" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Festinanter post concionum molem.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="20" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Tui observans.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="21" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Exemplaria literarum remitto.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="22" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Habeo gratias; legi cum voluptate; sunt Latinissimae, sed et exscripsi.</s>
					<s n="23" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Amplissimo viro d. <persName ref="p495" type="citizen_name" cert="high">Heinrycho Bullingero</persName>, domino et patrono suo summe observando.</s>
				</p>
			</div>
